rows.label: qst201909_0010
rows.name: There you are, you black-feathered ingrate!

rows.label: qst201909_0020
rows.name: Who are you?!

rows.label: qst201909_0030
rows.name:
First you swindle us, and now you have the gall
to make an innocent girl cry?! Scum of Alst!

rows.label: qst201909_0040
rows.name: Your wicked meddling ends here and now!

rows.label: qst201909_0050
rows.name: Who this woman? Why she make so much racket?

rows.label: qst201909_0060
rows.name: ...Ah, I remember her!

rows.label: qst201909_0070
rows.name: She dumdum who buy desert island for 1,000,000 gold!

rows.label: qst201909_0080
rows.name: Ahahahaha! That hilarious!

rows.label: qst201909_0090
rows.name: How stupid can woman be?!

rows.label: qst201909_0100
rows.name: Hahaha...

rows.label: qst201909_0110
rows.name:
Mocking an exalted figure, are you?
You ought to be put in your place.

rows.label: qst201909_0120
rows.name: We hope you are ready for your just deserts!

rows.label: qst201909_0130
rows.name: Desserts? We have plenty food already!

rows.label: qst201909_0140
rows.name: Nargh... What you gonna do about it?

rows.label: qst201909_0150
rows.name: Divine Punishment!

rows.label: qst201909_0160
rows.name:
Now, step forward if you'd like to be a forgotten page
in the annals of history!

rows.label: qst201909_0170
rows.name: W-wait! Calm down!

rows.label: qst201909_0180
rows.name:
There important reason why we
do what we do!

rows.label: qst201909_0190
rows.name:
There is nothing you could possibly say to allay
our righteous anger.

rows.label: qst201909_0200
rows.name: Prepare yourselves!

rows.label: qst201909_0210
rows.name: Whoa, whoa, hold on a second, Linne!

rows.label: qst201909_0220
rows.name:
Stay out of this, Rex! Or do you wish
to receive similar punishment?

rows.label: qst201909_0230
rows.name:
But if you beat these guys up, how are
you going to get your money back?

rows.label: qst201909_0240
rows.name: [ML:undisp ](gasp)

rows.label: qst201909_0250
rows.name: Indeed... The peon makes a fair point!

rows.label: qst201909_0260
rows.name:
We should at least listen to what
they've got to say.

rows.label: qst201909_0270
rows.name: You can always pummel them later, yeah?

rows.label: qst201909_0280
rows.name:
Oh, well... How could we refuse advice from
our dear friend Nia?

rows.label: qst201909_0290
rows.name: All right. We shall listen to your pitiful pleas.

rows.label: qst201909_0300
rows.name: However!

rows.label: qst201909_0310
rows.name:
If we perceive even the slightest hint of foul play,
you know what's coming to you, yes?

rows.label: qst201909_0320
rows.name: [ML:undisp ](timorous, fearful noise)
